data.description: Under Construction. Riviera Bella East, The Cali is a split-open-concept home features 1828 sq. ft. of living space and 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Enjoy the views from the covered lanai in your back yard. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining friends and family! The chef of the family will love the large center island, large pantry, Stainless steel 5 burner natural gas range. Never run out of hot water and save on your electric bill with a gas tankless hot water heater. Natural gas is a green feature that helps reduce our carbon footprint. Close to highways and major shopping, this home is located in the city of Debary 5 minutes from the Sunrail station. The Envera gated security system keeps you and your family safe. All homes come with smart home technology and a Ring doorbell to give you added security. Come home to Riviera Bella today! *Photos are of similar model but not that of exact house. Pictures, photographs, colors, features, and sizes are for illustration purposes only and will vary from the homes as built. Home and community information including pricing, included features, terms, availability and amenities are subject to change and prior sale at any time without notice or obligation. Please note that no representations or warranties are made regarding school districts or school assignments; you should conduct your own investigation regarding current and future schools and school boundaries. *
